SubjectRegulations Amending the Port Authorities Operations Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the PORT AUTHORITIES OPERATIONS REGULATIONS in order to increase the minimum remuneration rates for container trucking movements, to, from and within Port Metro Vancouver, by 12 percent as well as double the current fuel surcharge.
